{"tid":1864261,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"國內口罩供不應求　國民黨周錫瑋：進口就好啦！這麼簡單的事！","createTime":"2020-02-05T13:39:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T13:40:48.000Z","uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d3deed0aa5d5cd3931e95dbe112809c891e6e3a2","tid":1864261,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T13:39:03.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情持續升溫，台灣民眾瘋搶口罩，行政院長蘇貞昌拍板定案，從6日起將讓民眾使用健保卡在衛生所及健保特約藥局「實名制」購買，每個人7天內只能限購2片。消息一出立刻引發正反兩派論戰，對此，前台北縣長周錫瑋今（4）日表示，「全世界做口罩的國家這麼多，進口就好啦！進口口罩這麼簡單的事情！」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/news.aspx?newsid=682901\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D682901&d=SLV77eIUGxkMmCzjf2iStz%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=e958edfe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D682901&h=0519fab0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/news.aspx?newsid=682901</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實同林奠思維一樣，不過佢係得個講字，林奠真係走去&quot;買&quot;"},{"pid":"89db131420138f305612b41c8e23ff11a850c82f","tid":1864261,"uid":203955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T13:40:48.000Z","msg":"何不食肉糜2020版"}]}